    "Salbutamol": [
      {
        "text": "##### Type\nSynthetic \\u03b22 receptor stimulant [S4]\n\n##### Presentations\nPressurised metered dose inhaler (pMDI) – 100mcg per activation\n\n##### Actions\n\n- Bronchodilation\n\n- Relaxation of involuntary muscle\n\n- Moves K+ from extracellular to intracellular space\n\n#### Uses\n\n- Respiratory distress due to asthma or COPD\n\n- Emergency treatment of suspected hyperkalaemia \n\n#### Adverse Effects\n\n- Tachycardia\n\n- Tremors\n\n- Hypotension\n\n#### Contraindications\nKnown hypersensitivity \n\n#### Pregnancy and Breastfeeding##### Pregnancy\n- Safe to use\n\n##### Breastfeeding\n- Safe to use\n\n#### Doses#### Mild to moderate respiratory distress\n**pMDI via spacer**\n##### Adult ≥6 years\n- 4-12 actuations \n- Repeat every 20-30 minutes\n- 1 actuation to 4 breaths.\n\n##### Paediatric",
